<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <form action="/signup" method="POST">
      <label>회원가입</label><br />
      <input type="text" name="userid" placeholder="아이디" /><br />
      <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="이름" /><br />
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="패스워드" /><br />
      <input type="password" name="repassword" placeholder="패스워드" /><br />
      <input type="email" name="useremail" placeholder="email" /><br />
      <input type="tel" name="userphone" placeholder="연락처" /><br />
      <input type="text" name="address" placeholder="주소" /><br />
      <button type="button" onclick="findAddr()">주소찾기</button>
      <input type="text" name="detailAddress" placeholder="상세주소" /><br />
      <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
      <p>이미 가입되어 있으신가요? <a href="/login">Login</a></p>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
